name: Anaerobic Intensive 30sec x 5
description:
Today we step up the effort, but only briefly. By completing 5 x 30-second high-intensity efforts we will be tapping into our anaerobic reserves while recruiting a large number of fast-twitch fibres. With plenty of recovery between efforts, you should be hitting each interval fully recovered.
